You say you are poor because you don't know how to exploit the things around you.

0:05:43.940,0:05:50.040
There are so much blessings - you are in the midst of blessings.

0:05:50.040,0:05:54.120
You are in the midst of money - money is everywhere.

0:05:54.120,0:06:00.340
You need to be renewed in your spirit.

0:06:00.340,0:06:04.540
For how long shall we continue this...?

0:06:04.540,0:06:09.320
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:06:09.320,0:06:13.420
We are financially "buoyant" more than spiritual.

0:06:13.420,0:06:19.000
We are becoming more prosperous than spiritual.

0:06:19.000,0:06:23.060
That is a cause of your complaining.

0:06:23.060,0:06:39.140
Even if you have money, that complain will not go, that will not remove your nightmare, isolation or depression.

0:06:39.140,0:06:45.740
There are many sicknesses and afflictions for which there is no medicine.

0:06:45.740,0:06:49.580
You have money, you go to the doctor for the better treatment,

0:06:49.580,0:06:55.960
but there are many afflictions without medicine.

0:06:55.960,0:07:04.280
If you say money is the answer - what about afflictions without medicine?

0:07:04.280,0:07:13.480
These are curses - only God can remove them.

0:07:13.480,0:07:17.860
This new year, your spirit must be renewed.

0:07:17.860,0:07:21.580
When your spirit is renewed, you will discover yourself.

0:07:21.580,0:07:30.980
It is not your sweat or your labour that brings out that blessing you are talking about.

0:07:30.980,0:07:38.400
It is our relationship with God that causes this to happen.

0:07:38.400,0:07:45.440
When you are renewed spiritually, it will affect your family and children as well.

0:07:45.440,0:07:55.220
Ability to be able to put your challenges behind and meditate on Jesus - this is what you don't have.

0:07:55.220,0:08:04.720
Tell your neighbour, "Ability to be able to put your challenges behind and meditate on Jesus -

0:08:04.720,0:08:10.120
this is what we all lack."

0:08:10.120,0:08:16.160
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:08:16.160,0:08:23.080
