0:08:23.080,0:08:28.160
He said, "Put it behind because I have overcome for you."

0:08:28.160,0:08:31.860
But the ability to put it behind...

0:08:31.860,0:08:42.140
When you have a headache - ignore that headache and focus on Jesus - that is the ability we need now.

0:08:42.140,0:08:49.000
You cannot be meditating on your challenges and on Jesus at the same time.

0:08:49.000,0:08:53.160
The ability to be able to put behind our situation.

0:08:53.160,0:09:05.980
The situation is there: You have a serious headache but you are more of Jesus - with all your heart you are yearning for Jesus.

0:09:05.980,0:09:15.220
Just put that behind you: The ability to be able to do that is what we lack.

0:09:15.220,0:09:21.080
It seems that our challenges overcome us.

0:09:21.080,0:09:27.620
We want to worship God without challenges.

0:09:27.620,0:09:37.340
Ability to put our challenges aside and worship Him - our spirits must be renewed.

0:09:37.340,0:09:47.800
To renew our spirits, right now, begin to meditate on the Word -

0:09:47.800,0:09:54.880
turn it over and over and over in our hearts.

0:09:54.880,0:09:59.920
Meditate on it and turn it over and over.

0:09:59.920,0:10:03.820
Turn it over - don't let it go.

0:10:03.820,0:10:08.260
Continue to meditate on it.

0:10:08.260,0:10:10.660
Before you know it...

0:10:10.660,0:10:13.900
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:10:13.900,0:10:18.560
You are saturated already - before you know it.

0:10:18.560,0:10:26.040
You must prosper in your spiritual life first.

0:10:26.040,0:10:38.640
Get your spiritual life in order; that is where the power, ability of God lies.

0:10:38.640,0:10:48.440
There is nothing you have not enjoyed but the relationship with God, you've not enjoyed properly.

0:10:48.440,0:11:00.660
Everything: you enjoyed money, pleasure - but relationship with God in a proper way - you have not.

0:11:00.660,0:11:07.120
Why can't you put it before you and let it be your first priority?

0:11:07.120,0:11:13.480
There is nothing that can change you and bring what you are looking for.

0:11:13.480,0:11:18.340
That proper relationship.

0:11:18.340,0:11:26.460
It is time that you should know Him like children know their fathers.

0:11:26.460,0:11:29.280
Stop imagining Him: "Jesus said this...".

0:11:29.280,0:11:32.820
Somebody will tell you, "Jesus says this...".

0:11:32.820,0:11:38.240
You should be able to hear by yourself - it is time to hear this.

0:11:38.240,0:11:42.660
The life you live here is the life you are going to meet over there.

0:11:42.660,0:11:45.840
Don't let anybody tell you, "Heaven, Heaven...".

0:11:45.840,0:11:47.480
How do you live this life?

0:11:47.480,0:11:49.800
Heaven is reward.

0:11:49.800,0:11:53.920
What are you doing and expect a reward?

0:11:53.920,0:11:58.000
The file will be opened to you.

0:11:58.000,0:12:02.400
You are planting here - you will reap over there.

0:12:02.400,0:12:05.240
What are you planting?

0:12:05.240,0:12:11.420
Right now, our spiritual life is the first priority.

0:12:11.420,0:12:19.620
The money you are looking for, you can never have enough.

0:12:19.620,0:12:30.380
Tell your neighbour, “The wealth, possessions you are looking for, you can never have enough”.

0:12:30.380,0:12:38.820
Because we can never have enough, there is an urge to steal, to kill, and to destroy.

0:12:38.820,0:12:47.720
The urge - because we never can have enough money, possessions, and other things you are looking for.

0:12:47.720,0:12:53.200
It is not possible because there are always people above you.

0:12:53.200,0:12:58.380
In the spirit, in your relationship with God, there is a place for you.

0:12:58.380,0:13:01.540
There is a place for me, there is a place for you.

0:13:01.540,0:13:11.760
God purposely created a space for me, "OK, T.B. Joshua - this is yours. This is what to do".

0:13:11.760,0:13:12.780
This was only for me.

0:13:12.780,0:13:16.200
You too, you have your own space.

0:13:16.200,0:13:23.040
There is not much competition, that would make you to be having a...

0:13:23.040,0:13:27.720
... unless you are a "zero" - like at the level many of us are today.

0:13:27.720,0:13:31.560
You cannot sense or be filled.

0:13:31.560,0:13:38.680
The life we live is what moves us into what?

0:13:38.680,0:13:40.880
Jesus' name.

0:13:40.880,0:13:44.620
What kind of life are you living?

0:13:44.620,0:13:50.500
Jesus' name is not just something you can just come and claim, "Jesus, in Jesus..." - no.

0:13:50.500,0:13:57.660
The life you live is what moves you into Jesus’ name.

0:13:57.660,0:14:02.640
That is, in line with God’s Word.

0:14:02.640,0:14:09.220
It ushers us into calling Jesus.

0:14:09.220,0:14:14.560
You believe so much in majority, not God’s authority.

0:14:14.560,0:14:21.760
Create time for yourself to meet God.

0:14:21.760,0:14:29.880
You must cultivate this habit to meet God.

0:14:29.880,0:14:38.240
Talk to Him, even though at the beginning it is like, "whom am I talking to? I don't hear from Him.

0:14:38.240,0:14:40.020
