0:15:50.200,0:15:52.160
How do we test genuineness?

0:15:52.160,0:15:56.440
We test genuineness through challenges.

0:15:56.440,0:16:01.260
If your faith is not tested, it’s not real faith.

0:16:01.260,0:16:04.480
Our faith must be tested.

0:16:04.480,0:16:09.560
That is why we call it, ‘faith’.

0:16:09.560,0:16:22.360
